#: js/blocks/WidgetBlocks.js:135
#.TRANS: Attack time is the time taken for initial run-up of level from nil to peak, beginning when the key is first pressed.
#. AUTOTRANSLATED: Google Translate
msgid "attack"
msgstr "தாக்குதல்"


